---
---
<section class="py-32 bg-[#0B0C10]">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-20">
      <span class="font-label text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-[#FBB03B] mb-4 block">Depoimentos</span>
      <h2 class="font-headline text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white">O que dizem os clientes e montadores.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 border-t-2 border-white/10 hover:border-[#FBB03B] transition-colors duration-500">
        <div class="flex gap-1 mb-6">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#FBB03B] text-sm">star</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#FBB03B] text-sm">star</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#FBB03B] text-sm">star</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#FBB03B] text-sm">star</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#FBB03B] text-sm">star</span>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-white/70 mb-8 italic leading-relaxed">
          "Economizei em torno de 65% perto de outros orçamentos. Tudo muito rápido e prático, graças ao seu grande conhecimento."
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white/50">person</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-headline font-bold text-sm text-white">Ricardo Colleti</p>
            <p class="font-label text-[10px] uppercase text-white/40">Cliente</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 border-t-2 border-white/10 hover:border-[#FBB03B] transition-colors duration-500">
        <div class="flex gap-1 mb-6">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#FBB03B] text-sm">star</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#FBB03B] text-sm">star</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#FBB03B] text-sm">star</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#FBB03B] text-sm">star</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#FBB03B] text-sm">star</span>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-white/70 mb-8 italic leading-relaxed">
          "O detalhamento facilita demais o trabalho do montador... economizei mais de 40%. Se o montador tiver experiência, o sucesso é garantido."
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white/50">person</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-headline font-bold text-sm text-white">Daniel Mendes</p>
            <p class="font-label text-[10px] uppercase text-white/40">Cliente</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
      <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 border-t-2 border-white/10 hover:border-[#FBB03B] transition-colors duration-500">
        <div class="flex gap-1 mb-6">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#FBB03B] text-sm">star</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#FBB03B] text-sm">star</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#FBB03B] text-sm">star</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#FBB03B] text-sm">star</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[#FBB03B] text-sm">star</span>
        </div>
        <p class="font-body text-white/70 mb-8 italic leading-relaxed">
          "O próprio montador elogiou o projeto. Tivemos paredes fora de esquadro, mas eles conseguiram adaptar perfeitamente por causa do projeto."
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white/50">person</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-headline font-bold text-sm text-white">Carmém Wander</p>
            <p class="font-label text-[10px] uppercase text-white/40">Cliente</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
